column5: Well i just wanted to say a early happy canada day to all you ONFNER'S out they're.....I am sure many of you like myself have much planned....I am 1st having a big yard sale in the morning then will be heading out to fish the rest of the day. Sunday pretty much the same thing fish as well as monday...  ..  So i hope you all enjoy the festivities no matter where you are & have a fantabulous weekend  Nautifish

Well to all the same,have a safe and great long weekend.Tonight it,s Travis Tritt with the mrs,s and the other lady,sorry Terry, wish you were there.LOL Then it,s some late day smallies on Saturday then some river buckets on sunday,then more smallies on Monday.  Have a good one all.

Hope your sale goes well, you can buy more fishing stuff!!!!!!!!! Fishing Saturday Lake Erie, hope to catch my first walleye out of there???? Lake Ontario Sunday with the Rib Fest afterwards and Monday Lake Ontario again....  Have a great weekend everyone.  Be careful out there.

Ah yes the Ribfest.Coming to Barrie soon.Great event.  6th Annual Ribfest and Craft Beer Show July 12, 2007 Memorial Square  The 6th Annual Downtown Barrie Ribfest and Craft Beer Show is happening Thursday July 12th through to Sunday July 15th 2007 in Memorial Square! A wide selection of Ribs, Chicken and all the great samples of local area Craft breweries.
Yes, do have a safe and enjoyable weekend...please leave toronto   I am working Saturday, likely Sunday overtime and Monday..who knows...may get onto G. Bay for a bit.  Maureen
